		<title>Google Books の Library Book Scan すら Fair Use と言われたのに...</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://text.baldanders.info/remark/2015/google-books-library-project/" />
		<id>tag:text.Baldanders.info,2015-11-01:/remark/2015/google-books-library-project/</id>
